## Layout fields

Unlike other field types which collect information, layout fields are used to organize and display information in the submission form user interface.

![](data:image/png;base64,)

## UI Step

Is used to split the submission form into multiple steps

## UI Image

Is used to add an image to the submission form e.g information or cosmetic reasons

## UI Heading

Is used to insert a Heading into the form between fields e.g to provide information or to create distinction between fields

## UI HTML

Is used to insert HTML code within the form
